# React Fitness4U App

## Description

Welcome to the React Fitness App! This app is designed to help you reach your fitness goals by providing a platform for creating workouts, assigning exercises from an external database, and tracking your progress in a calendar. It also offers a way to calculate your body type and daily macronutrient intake based on your specific objectives. 

With different user roles available (Utilizadores, Personal Trainers, and Admin), each with their own options for creating and accessing user information, the React Fitness App is versatile and user-friendly. Built with React, Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, and Tailwind, this app is simple yet powerful.


## Usage

To use the React Fitness App, follow these steps:

1. Create an account or log in with an existing account.
2. Create a new workout by clicking on the "Create Workout" button.
3. Assign exercises to the workout by searching the exercise database and selecting the desired exercises.
4. Assign the workout to a day in the calendar by clicking  the workout to the desired day.
5. View your progress in the calendar and track your body type and daily macronutrient intake based on your fitness goals.

## Credits

- Exercise database provided by [Exercise API](https://rapidapi.com/justin-WFnsXH_t6/api/exercisedb)
